# pack/repack input folders + generate output
# bundles), the canonical Node ZIP archive
# library by Stuart Knightley (Stuk) -
# github.com/Stuk/jszip.
#
# Stuart Knightley's jszip is the de-facto
# canonical Node + browser ZIP archive library:
#   - 45,000,000+ weekly npm downloads
#   - Isomorphic: same API works in browser +
#     Node + Deno + Bun
