#     write
#   - Built-in deflate compression (delegates
#     to pako, Vitaly Puzrin's pure-JS zlib
#     port from Axis 262 YAML's nodeca/js-yaml
#     same author)
#   - File entry filtering by glob/regex
#   - Per-file compression-level overrides
#   - Comment preservation (archive-level +
#     per-entry)
#   - Time-stamp + permission preservation
#   - Streaming output via Node Streams
